OL,3,CParents demand car design changes
OL,4,Cafter boy crushed to death in parking
OL,5,Caccident
OL,7,FThe parents of a young boy who died
OL,8,Fafter being crushed between two
OL,9,Fvehicles are calling for an overhaul
OL,10,Fof electric car design.
OL,12,FAlfie Tollett was trapped between two
OL,13,Fcars when the driver of a Jaguar I-
OL,14,FPace pressed the wrong button and put
OL,15,Fthe car into drive instead of reverse.
OL,17,FAlfie, who was just seven years old,
OL,18,Fhad been putting on his rugby boots at
OL,19,FPlymstock Albion Oaks RFC in Plymouth
OL,20,Fwhen the incident happened in February
OL,21,Flast year.
