OL,4,Cafter boy crushed to death in parking
OL,5,Caccident
OL,7,FAn inquest has now heard the driver of
OL,8,Fthe #70,000 Jaguar I-Pace was trying
OL,9,Fto straighten up as he parked behind a
OL,10,Fnearby van.
OL,12,FInstead of hitting the reverse button,
OL,13,Fhe pushed the forward button. This
OL,14,Fmeant that the car moved forward as he
OL,15,Fpressed the accelerator, trapping
OL,16,FAlfie.
OL,18,FAn inquest in Devon heard that Alfie
OL,19,Fsuffered fatal crush injuries to his
OL,20,Fchest.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
