OL,4,Cafter boy crushed to death in parking
OL,5,Caccident
OL,7,FThe driver was not prosecuted because
OL,8,Fhe died from natural causes shortly
OL,9,Fafter the incident.
OL,11,FAlfie's parents, Stephen and Gemma
OL,12,FTollett, are now calling on Jaguar
OL,13,FLand Rover to change what they see as
OL,14,Fa "design fault" to ensure no-one else
OL,15,Fsuffers a similar tragedy.
OL,17,F"There is so much we could say about
OL,18,FAlfie, but we just want everyone to
OL,19,Fknow he was our amazing, cheeky,
OL,20,Fprecious little boy who we all miss
OL,21,Fand love so very much," they said.
