OL,7,F"Alfie's memory will always be kept
OL,8,Fgoing through his two brothers and
OL,9,Fsister. Keep chasing the Pokemons,
OL,10,Friding the unicorns, and scoring the
OL,11,Fgoals up there our special Alfie Moo.
OL,13,F"We'd like to thank everyone who has
OL,14,Fsent kind messages of support for our
OL,15,Ffamily since that terrible day. Alfie
OL,16,Fwill be forever in our hearts.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
