OL,7,F"We thank the coroner for her findings
OL,8,Fand the confirmation that she will
OL,9,Fwrite to Jaguar Land Rover about
OL,10,Fwhether additional steps can be taken
OL,11,Fto make this electric car safer.
OL,13,F"We would welcome anything that
OL,14,Fprevents any other family from having
OL,15,Fto go through what we have as a
OL,16,Ffamily, and that includes all
OL,17,Fmanufacturers of electric vehicles to
OL,18,Freview their control designs in light
OL,19,Fof this case.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
