OL,7,F"We have lost our beautiful son Alfie
OL,8,Fbecause of what we see as a design
OL,9,Fflaw and we are passionate for this to
OL,10,Fnever happen again."
OL,12,FThe inquest concluded a verdict of
OL,13,Faccidental death.
OL,15,FHowever, Deborah Archer - assistant
OL,16,Fcoroner for Devon, Plymouth and Torbay
OL,17,F- said she was concerned about the
OL,18,Fdesign of the car.
