OL,7,FCurrently, the car can be switched
OL,8,Fbetween the two by simply pressing one
OL,9,Fof two buttons on a console.
OL,11,FShe said: "There were a number of
OL,12,Ferrors that were made by the driver
OL,13,Fwhich caused or contributed to the
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,F"However, these errors occurred as a
OL,17,Fresult of there being no intermediary
OL,18,Fstep within the Jaguar I-Pace being
OL,19,Fnecessary to put the car into drive/
OL,20,Freverse other than pressing a button.
