OL,7,F"In the police officer's opinion, if
OL,8,Fthere had also been a lever or
OL,9,Fsomething similar present in the
OL,10,Fvehicle that needed to be engaged
OL,11,Fbefore a button was pressed this may
OL,12,Fhave alerted the drive to the fact
OL,13,Fthat he had pushed the incorrect
OL,14,Fbutton on the three-button console."
OL,16,FWriting to the chief executive of
OL,17,FJaguar Land Rover, she said there is a
OL,18,Frisk more deaths could occur "unless
OL,19,Faction is taken".
