OL,7,FJaguar Land Rover has until 22 October
OL,8,Fto respond to the coroner's concerns.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the manufacturer said:
OL,11,F"We have received correspondence from
OL,12,Fthe coroner and shall be responding in
OL,13,Fdue course.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts and sympathies, however,
OL,16,Fare with the family of Alfie Tollett
OL,17,Ffollowing his accidental death."
