OL,7,FHollie Muckley, from law firm HCC, who
OL,8,Fsupported the family at the inquest,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The coroner has now formally
OL,10,Fconcluded the inquest and, although
OL,11,Fthis was hugely challenging for the
OL,12,Ffamily, it has gone some way to
OL,13,Fanswering key questions they had about
OL,14,Fthe circumstances.
OL,16,F"The family await the response from
OL,17,FJaguar Land Rover in relation to the
OL,18,Fprevention of future deaths order
OL,19,Finstructed by the coroner."
